Details:

  name: REST-like API server for Lindat Services 
  documentation: https://redmine.ms.mff.cuni.cz/projects/lindat-services
  maintainers: Jozef M., Loganathan

Description:

Server is implemented in python over Cherrypy framework using plugin based applications inside the applications directory.

How to start:
  
  1) move project_settings.py.example to project_settings.py
  
  2) ensure python & others is installed
  
    > python main.py --version
    
  3) run it as deamon, se example scripts in `scripts` directory 